Come support independent film! Join us at @lashortsfest on July 25th to watch @tothedeathfilm on the big screen! 

We are grateful that we are still able to share our little short with a big message. Directed by the incredible @imrosemciver , this story is based on our personal experience of auditioning while brown… and how the lack of roles for diverse actors had us feeling like we needed to kill each other to succeed.

We hope this film spreads love and empowers those who watch it. 

#SAGstrong #WGAstrong
